ch You Would Have Made Owning Oracle Stock In The Last 15 Years", "id": 26742222, "images": [{"size": "large", "url": "https://cdn.benzinga.com/files/imagecache/2048x1536xUP/images/story/2022/valuestock_image_937.jpeg"}, {"size": "small", "url": "https://cdn.benzinga.com/files/imagecache/1024x768xUP/images/story/2022/valuestock_image_937.jpeg"}, {"size": "thumb", "url": "https://cdn.benzinga.com/files/imagecache/250x187xUP/images/story/2022/valuestock_image_937.jpeg"}], "source": "benzinga", "summary": "Oracle (NYSE:ORCL) has outperformed the market over the past 15 years by 2.58% on an annualized basis producing an average annual return of 10.15%. Currently, Oracle has a market capitalization of $217.40 billion. ", "symbols": ["ORCL"], "updated_at": "2022-04-21T15:32:31Z", "url": "https://www.benzinga.com/news/earnings/22/04/26742222/heres-how-much-you-would-have-made-owning-oracle-stock-in-the-last-15-years"}, {"author": "Benzinga Insights", "content": "", "created_at": "2022-04-22T20:10:12Z", "headline": "How Is The Market Feeling About Oracle Corporation?", "id": 26771256, "images": [{"size": "large", "url": "https://cdn.benzinga.com/files/imagecache/2048x1536xUP/images/story/2022/movers_image_7154.jpeg"}, {"size": "small", "url": "https://cdn.benzinga.com/files/imagecache/1024x768xUP/images/story/2022/movers_image_7154.jpeg"}, {"size": "thumb", "url": "https://cdn.benzinga.com/files/imagecache/250x187xUP/images/story/2022/movers_image_7154.jpeg"}], "source": "benzinga", "summary": "Oracle Corporation&#39;s (NYSE:ORCL) short percent of float has risen 26.83% since its last report. The company recently reported that it has 23.66 million shares sold short, which is 1.56% of all regular shares that are available for trading.", "symbols": ["ORCL"], "updated_at": "2022-04-22T20:10:13Z", "url": "https://www.benzinga.com/short-sellers/22/04/26771256/how-is-the-market-feeling-about-oracle-corporation"}]